*PCB*        GENERAL PARAMETERS OF THE PCB DESIGN

UNITS        0              2=Inches 1=Metric 0=Mils
USERGRID     10     10      Space between USER grid points
MAXIMUMLAYER 4              Maximum routing layer 
WORKLEVEL    26             Level items will be created on
DISPLAYLEVEL 1              toggle for displaying working level last
LAYERPAIR    1      4       Layer pair used to route connection
VIAMODE      T              Type of via to use when routing between layers
LINEWIDTH    8              Width items will be created with
TEXTSIZE     70     10      Height and LineWidth text will be created with
JOBTIME      62028          Amount of time spent on this PCB design
DOTGRID      200    200     Space between graphic dots
SCALE        20.365          Scale of window expansion
ORIGIN       11885  11270   User defined origin location
WINDOWCENTER 12835  12020   Point defining the center of the window
